                    </div>
                    <span>I really enjoyed this book and would have given it 5 stars.  However, I think the author could have used Bartimaeus more in the dialogue.  He wasn't developed enough in this book.  There wasn't enough interaction between Bartimaeus and Nathaniel, and too much time on Nathaniel's job in the government.  All in all it was a good read.  I stayed up late for several nights reading it.</span>
                  
              
